OL,3,CMotorcylist dies after Cushendall crash
OL,5,FA motorcylist has died following a two-
OL,6,Fvehicle collision in Cushendall, Co
OL,7,FAntrim.
OL,9,FThe man died at the scene of the crash
OL,10,Fon the Chapel Road shortly before 1pm
OL,11,Fon Sunday.
OL,13,FThe 55-year-old was from the Bellaghy
OL,14,Farea.
OL,16,FThe road which was closed for a time,
OL,17,Fhas since reopened.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
