OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782737333
OL,3,CMotorcylist dies after Cushendall crash
OL,5,FDetective Inspector Stewart, from the
OL,6,FCollision Investigation Unit, said:
OL,7,F"Shortly before 1pm, police received
OL,8,Fand responded to a report of a two
OL,9,Fvehicle collision on the Chapel Road.
OL,11,F"Colleagues from other emergency
OL,12,Fservices were also in attendance.
OL,14,F"Sadly, the male rider of a
OL,15,Fmotorcycle, who was 55 years old, and
OL,16,Ffrom the Bellaghy area, died at the
OL,17,Fscene.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
