PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782737333
OL,3,CMotorcylist dies after Cushendall crash
OL,5,F"The Chapel Road, which was closed in
OL,6,Fboth directions as enquiries were
OL,7,Fconducted, has now re-opened to
OL,8,Fmotorists.
OL,10,F"Enquiries remain ongoing this
OL,11,Fmorning, and we are appealing to
OL,12,Fanyone with information about the
OL,13,Fcollision, or who has dash-cam footage
OL,14,Fof what happened, to contact police."
